92ee052f-7a28-4506-b9e7-2e7b566c1b44.text: Mission EVO is the first mobile survival game developed with Unreal Engine 5. It will be released in 2023. THE WORLD HAS BEEN RUINED. RAID FOR EMBERS, FIGHT FOR SURVIVAL! In this open world known as Emberland, the only aim is to survive... till the very end. Danger lurks around every corner, everything wants you dead. You have to survive through the cruelest of competition - not only against all kinds of mutant creatures, but against hundreds of other desperate players. Keep in mind, by hook or by crook, everything goes! But being alive is always the aim of the game. The light of Ember is guiding your way. Embark on this fantastic journey, NOW!
